thread.title: BRIEF-Morphosys, Galapagos initiate IGUANA phase 2 clinical trial with Mor106 in Atopic Dermatitis patients

title: BRIEF-Morphosys, Galapagos initiate IGUANA phase 2 clinical trial with Mor106 in Atopic Dermatitis patients
text:
May 1, 2018 / 8:27 PM / Updated 11 minutes ago BRIEF-Morphosys, Galapagos initiate IGUANA phase 2 clinical trial with Mor106 in Atopic Dermatitis patients Reuters Staff 1 Min Read
May 1 (Reuters) - Morphosys Ag:
* DGAP-NEWS: MORPHOSYS AND GALAPAGOS ANNOUNCE INITIATION OF THE IGUANA PHASE 2 CLINICAL TRIAL WITH MOR106 IN ATOPIC DERMATITIS PATIENTS
* PLACEBO CONTROLLED, DOUBLE-BLIND STUDY WILL EVALUATE EFFICACY, SAFETY AND PHARMACOKINETICS (PK) OF MOR106 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
